{"an4.144:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 4.144 ","an4.144:0.2":"15. Abhavagga ","an4.144:0.3":"Obhasasutta ","an4.144:1.1":"“Cattarome, bhikkhave, obhasa. ","an4.144:1.2":"Katame cattaro? ","an4.144:1.3":"Candobhaso, suriyobhaso, aggobhaso, pannobhaso—","an4.144:1.4":"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattaro obhasa. ","an4.144:1.5":"Etadaggam, bhikkhave, imesam catunnam obhasanam yadidam pannobhaso”ti. ","an4.144:1.6":"Catuttham. "}